      public Level3(int timer, int charX, int charY, int bgX, int bgY, boolean lockCamX, boolean lockCamY, ArrayList<MazeObject> obj, ArrayList<MazeObject> collected) throws IOException
      Class constructor, used when returning to level 3 from minigame
      Parameters:
      timer - The time remaining
      charX - The player's X position
      charY - The player's Y position
      bgX - The background's X position
      bgY - The background's Y position
      lockCamX - Whether the camera's X movement is locked
      lockCamY - Whether the camera's Y movement is locked
      obj - The list of interactable objects
      collected - The list of objects collected
